= Image Properties
  [topic]
@link[guide >index#additional-features]

@desc View detailed properties of the selected image.

Image Viewer allows users to view an image's properties. All images will have the following
basic properties:

* Image size
* Image format
* File size
* File creation date
* File modification date

If the file has $link[href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exif"](Exif) metadata, it
will be shown below the basic properties.

To view the selected image's properties, press the $gui(Image Properties)
($media[type="image" src="figures/help-about-symbolic.svg"](help-about-symbolic)) button.